data.description: Looking for renovated and move in ready home?  Look no further.  This home has been renovated in the past 2 years.  Full list available but includes new paint in and out, completely renovated kitchen, refinished hardwoods and more.  This open floor plan home is great for entertaining. Kitchen is a MUST SEE - with wall of oversize kitchen cabinets, large single basin sink, quartz counters and open to the main level.  Features master suite on the main level with his/her closets, sitting room, fireplace, separate vanities and jetted tub.  3 Bedrooms upstairs with 1 being a large bedroom/bonus room making a great suite/rec room.  Don't overlook the full foot print basement with a 5th bedroom (Just needs flooring) almost ready and plenty of space to finish or storage. Garage is clean and offers epoxy floors.  Large .92 acre lot with storage/out building and fenced lot.  All of this and located close to Lake Allatoona (Walk to the lake) and 10 minutes to Cartersville or Canton.  If you are tired of looking at fixer uppers and homes needing TLC, then come see this gorgeous home.  Home owners have looked into every detail to give you the HGTV/magazine experience.
